22Foreign%20Countries%20Also%20Know%20%26quot%3BAayega%20Toh%20Modi%20Hi%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20At%20Key%20BJP%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20reasserted%20that%20his%20party%20BJP%20will%20return%20to%20power%20in%20general%20elections%20this%20summer%2C%20a%20win%20that%20will%20ensure%20a%20comfortable%20third%20term%20for%20him.%20He%20said%20that%20even%20foreign%20countries%20know%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eaayega%20toh%3C%2Fem%3E%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Ehi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Modi%20will%20return%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20BJP%20national%20convention%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20elections%20are%20yet%20to%20happen%20but%20I%20already%20have%20invitations%20from%20foreign%20countries%20for%20July%2C%20August%2C%20and%20September.%20What%20does%20this%20imply%3F%20It%20means%20that%20various%20nations%20around%20the%20world%20are%20entirely%20confident%20about%20the%20return%20of%20the%20BJP%20government.%20They%20also%20know%20-%20aayega%20toh%20Modi%20hi.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20said%20he%20was%20not%20seeking%20a%20third%20term%20to%20enjoy%20power%2C%20but%20to%20work%20for%20the%20nation.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20had%20thought%20of%20my%20home%2C%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20to%20build%20homes%20for%20crores%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20workers%20who%20gathered%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20for%20the%20key%20party%20meet%20that%20next%20100%20days%20are%20very%20crucial.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%20100%20days%2C%20you%20need%20to%20connect%20with%20every%20new%20voter%2C%20reach%20every%20beneficiary%2C%20every%20section%2C%20every%20community%2C%20and%20every%20person%20who%20believes%20in%20every%20religion.%20We%20need%20to%20gain%20the%20trust%20of%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PM%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20his%20government's%20ten%20years%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20India%20has%20achieved%20unprecedented%20momentum%20and%20gained%20the%20courage%20to%20achieve%20significant%20goals.%20India%20has%20reached%20new%20heights%20in%20every%20sector%20today%2C%20connecting%20every%20citizen%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20great%20determination.%20And%20this%20determination%20is%20-%20a%20developed%20India.%20We%20must%20make%20India%20developed%2C%20and%20in%20this%2C%20the%20next%205%20years%20will%20play%20a%20significant%20role.%20In%20the%20next%205%20years%2C%20India%20must%20work%20at%20a%20much%20faster%20pace%20than%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20citing%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20%26quot%3Bab%20ki%20paar%2C%20400%20paar%26quot%3B%20gaffe%20in%20the%20Parliament%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20even%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20chanting%20slogans%20of%20the%20NDA%20government%20crossing%20the%20400-mark.%20And%20for%20NDA%20to%20cross%20400%2C%20BJP%20must%20surpass%20the%20milestone%20of%20370.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20coalition%20won%20more%20than%20350%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20election.%20But%20PM%20Modi%20and%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20proclaimed%20that%20this%20time%20they%20are%20looking%20beyond%20400%20seats%2C%20making%20it%20the%20most%20decisive%20victory%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20his%20tirade%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20sin%20of%20Congress%20is%20that%20it%20has%20not%20hesitated%20to%20break%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20country's%20armed%20forces.%20Congress%20has%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20causing%20damage%20to%20India's%20national%20security%20and%20military%20strength%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20holding%20the%20two-day%20convention%20as%20part%20of%20its%20preparations%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20inaugural%20day%20of%20the%20national%20convention%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20BJP%20passed%20a%20political%20resolution%20titled%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%2C%20highlighting%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20Centre%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20It%20asserted%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20return%20for%20a%20third%20term%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20carry%20forward%20its%20roadmap%20for%20%26quot%3Bholistic%20development%20and%20welfare%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708254000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fpegnh47c_pm-modi-ani_625x300_18_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-bjp-convention-lok-sabha-elections-2024-foreign-countries-also-know-aayega-toh-modi-hi-pm-modi-at-key-bjp-meet-5081147%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20reasserted%20that%20his%20party%20BJP%20will%20return%20to%20power%20in%20general%20elections%20this%20summer%2C%20a%20win%20that%20will%20ensure%20a%20comfortable%20third%20term%20for%20him.%20He%20said%20that%20even%20foreign%20countries%20know%20that%20%26quot%3Baayega%20toh%20Modi%20hi%20(Modi%20w%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-bjp-convention-lok-sabha-elections-2024-foreign-countries-also-know-aayega-toh-modi-hi-pm-modi-at-key-bjp-meet-5081147%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Imran%20Khan's%20supporters%2C%20police%20clash%20over%20Pakistan%20polls%20rigging%20allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708253943000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107796639%2Cimgsize-1320998.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fimran-khans-supporters-clash-with-police-over-pakistan-polls-rigging-allegations%2Farticleshow%2F10