lf%3F%20According%20to%20the%20head%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tools-changing-content-creators-work-2024-1%23notion-is-an-ai-enhanced-connected-workspace-for-project-management-and-document-creation-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-powered%20transcription%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20company%2C%20that%20could%20become%20a%20reality%2C%20and%20sooner%20than%20we%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20prototype%20can%20be%20made%20working%20later%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Liang%20told%20Business%20Insider%2C%20adding%20that%20Otter%20has%20already%20made%20progress%20toward%20that%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20models%20are%20generally%20trained%20using%20a%20set%20of%20data%20to%20get%20them%20to%20behave%20in%20human-like%20ways.%20AI%20avatars%20should%20be%20trained%20on%20the%20recorded%20meeting%20notes%20and%20voice%20data%20of%20the%20specific%20people%20they're%20trying%20to%20replicate%2C%20Liang%20said%2C%20so%20that%20they%20can%20act%20and%20converse%20exactly%20like%20them.%20Once%20they%20have%20enough%20information%2C%20the%20avatars%20(in%20theory)%20will%20be%20able%20to%20speak%20in%20the%20cadence%20of%20individual%20workers%2C%20participate%20in%20conversations%2C%20and%20answer%20questions%20based%20on%20the%20worker's%20unique%20perspectives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiang%20expects%20Otter's%20AI%20work%20persona%20will%20be%20able%20to%20answer%2090%25%20of%20the%20questions%20it's%20asked%20during%20meetings%2C%20he%20said.%20When%20it's%20stuck%20on%20the%20remaining%2010%25%2C%20the%20questions%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20human%20worker%20with%20a%20note%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20answer%20this%20question%20%E2%80%94%20can%20you%20help%20me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20avatars%20can%20accurately%20represent%20employees%2C%20Liang%20said%20they'll%20save%20them%20time%20and%20boost%20productivity.%20He%20said%20the%20bots%20will%20be%20able%20to%20attend%20meetings%20related%20to%20customer%20support%2C%20sales%2C%20and%20team%20status%20updates%20%E2%80%94%20which%20could%20give%20employees%20extra%20hours%20in%20their%20day%20to%20focus%20on%20more%20creative%20tasks%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20make%20companies%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20could%20even%20send%20their%20virtual%20replicas%20to%20meetings%20that%20occur%20while%20they're%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20road%20to%20building%20trustworthy%20AI%20avatars%20is%20riddled%20with%20technical%20and%20social%20obstacles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20%26quot%3Bvery%20challenging%2C%26quot%3B%20Liang%20said%2C%20to%20get%20a%20model%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20right%20way%20to%20interact%20with%20a%20group%20of%20people%2C%20whether%20it's%20knowing%20when%20to%20speak%20up%2C%20wait%20its%20turn%2C%20or%20interject.%20That's%20because%20meeting%20etiquette%20varies%20based%20on%20what's%20being%20discussed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20notes%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20instill%20emotional%20cues%20into%20AI%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20determine%20whether%20the%20persona%20should%20raise%20its%20voice%20or%20stay%20calm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20needs%20to%20have%20the%20knowledge%20and%20emotional%20intelligence%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20productive%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Liang%20said%20about%20the%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20Liang%20believes%20any%20personas%20will%20need%20to%20go%20through%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20stages%26quot%3B%20before%20they%20can%20operate%20in%20the%20way%20he%20envisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Liang%20believes%20the%20technology%20to%20create%20them%20already%20exists.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-characterai-ceo-noam-shazeer-chatbot-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECharacter.ai%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20created%20AI%20personality%20chatbots%20that%20can%20speak%20like%20high-profile%20figures%20such%20as%20Elon%2