%3EThe%20risks%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20can%20seem%20overwhelming%20%E2%80%94%20for%20every%20benefit%20the%20technology%20provides%2C%20there's%20an%20adverse%20use.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOne%20major%20problem%20created%20by%20AI%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-deepfake%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeepfakes%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20videos%2C%20images%2C%20or%20audio%20generated%20by%20AI%20that%20can%20be%20designed%20to%20mimic%20a%20victim%20saying%20or%20doing%20something%20that%20never%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20deepfakes%20superimpose%20a%20likeness%20onto%20real%20video%20footage%2C%20while%20others%20are%20completely%20computer-generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202019%20study%20called%20The%20State%20of%20Deepfakes%20by%20Deep%20Trace%20found%20that%2096%25%20of%20deepfake%20videos%20were%20pornographic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHenry%20Ajder%2C%20a%20deepfakes%20researcher%20who%20coauthored%20that%20study%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20while%20the%20figure%20may%20have%20changed%2C%20the%20problem%20remains%20just%20as%20acute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20tools%20such%20as%20Dall-E%2C%20Stable%20Diffusion%2C%20and%20Midjourney%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbytedance-ai-model-speak-in-another-persons-voice-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20more%20widely%20accessible%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20becoming%20easier%20for%20people%20with%20very%20little%20technical%20knowledge%20to%20create%20deepfakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overall%20percentage%20is%20now%20lower%2C%20but%20the%20overall%20volume%20of%20deepfake%20content%20which%20is%20pornographic%20has%20exploded%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajder%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20talking%20about%20millions%20of%20victims%20around%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20content%20is%20fake%2C%20the%20humiliation%2C%20sense%20of%20trauma%2C%20and%20intimidation%20for%20victims%20are%20very%20real.%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22%23fef586%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fmark%3E%3Cbr%3EA%20British%20teenager%20killed%20herself%20in%202021%20after%20deepfake%20pornographic%20images%20of%20her%20were%20created%20and%20shared%20by%20other%20students%20from%20her%20school%20in%20a%20Snapchat%20group%2C%20BBC%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Swift%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b389756c8f0a134f7a2224%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDeepfake%20porn%20of%20pop%20superstar%20Taylor%20Swift%20has%20raised%20awareness%20of%20the%20issue.%3Cp%3EAxelle%2FBauer-Griffin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20deepfake%20porn%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%20started%20circulating%20online%2C%20prompting%20Elon%20Musk%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-fake-ai-images-searches-blocked-elon-musk-x-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eban%20searches%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20pop%20superstar%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20might%20seem%20grim%2C%20but%20there%20are%20tools%20and%20methods%20available%20that%20can%20help%20protect%20against%20AI%20manipulation%20of%20your%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeepfake%20detection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDigital%20watermarks%2C%20where%20content%20is%20clearly%20labeled%20as%20AI-generated%2C%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-cryptographically-verify-official-communications-ai-deep-fakes-surge-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsed%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20one%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20labels%20aim%20to%20both%20raise%20public%20awareness%20and%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20platforms%20to%20scrape%20and%20remove%20damaging%20fake%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-photo-search-tool-helps-identify-ai-generated-fake-images-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmeta-to-launch-ai-image-label-on-facebook-instagram-threads-1033036612%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20both%20announced%20plans%20to%20start%20labeling%20material%20created%20or%20modified%20by%20AI%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20credential%26quot%3B%20to%20make%20the%20origins%20of%20content%20clearer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-adding-digital-watermarks-ai-images-deepfakes-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20ChatGPT%20and%20the%20image%20generator%20DALL-E%2C%20plans%20to%20include%20both%20a%20visual%20watermark%20and%20hidden%20metadata%20that%20reveals%20the%20history%20of%20an%20image%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Coalition%20for%20Content%20Provenance%20and%20Authenticity%20(C2PA)%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DALL-E%202%20AI-generated%20image%20of%20a%20young%20woman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6554a3ac4ca513d824299fdf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI-generated%20image%20of%20a%20young%20woman%3Cp%3EOpen%20AI%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20dedicated%20platforms%20designed%20to%20check%20the%20origins%20of%20online%20material.%20%3Cu%3ESensity%3C%2Fu%3E%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20the%202019%20study%20on%20deepfakes%2C%20has%20developed%20a%20detection%20service%20that%20alerts%20users%20via%20email%20when%20they're%20watching%20content%20with%20telltale%20AI-generated%20fingerprints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20when%20an%20image%20may%20be%20obviously%20fake%20%E2%80%94%20as%20most%20still%20lack%20watermarks%20%E2%80%94%20the%20subject%20may%20still%20feel%20victimized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Poison%20pills'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDefensive%20tools%20that%20protect%20images%20from%20manipulation%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20stronger%20solution%2C%20though%20they're%20still%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20tools%20give%20users%20the%20option%20to%20process%20their%20images%20with%20an%20imperceptible%20signal%20that%2C%20when%20run%20through%20any%20AI-powered%20system%2C%20creates%20an%20unusable%2C%20blurry%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Nightshade%2C%20a%20tool%20created%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%2C%20adds%20pixels%20to%20images%20that%20corrupt%20when%20fed%20to%20an%20AI%20but%20leaves%20the%20image%20looking%20as%20intended%20for%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20think%20of%20Nightshade%20as%20adding%20a%20small%20poison%20pill%20inside%20an%20artwork%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20it's%20literally%20trying%20to%20confuse%20the%20training%20model%20on%20what%20is%20actually%20in%20the%20image%2C%26quot%3B%20Ben%20Zhao%2C%20one%20of%20the%20researchers%2C%20told%20NPR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227937%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20visit%20the%20World%20of%20AI%C2%B7magination%20exhibition%20at%20the%20Artechouse%20in%20New%20York%2C%20United%20States%20on%20February%2001%2C%202024.%20World%20of%20AI%C2%B7magination%20is%20Artechouse%20Studio's%20latest%20venture%20into%20the%20dynamic%20world%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20large-scale%20experiential%20digital%20artwork.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ccb75994aa8ee8e84b27a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225291%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20World%20of%20AI%C2%B7magination%20exhibition%20in%20New%20York%2C%20created%20using%20generative%20AI.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%20%2F%20Getty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20designed%20to%20protect%20artists'%20IP%2C%20the%20technology%20can%20work%20on%20any%20photograph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20really%20nice%20frontline%20defense%20for%20people%20to%20feel%20like%2C%20okay%2C%20I'm%20safe%20uploading%20photos%20from%20my%20friend's%20birthday%20that%20weekend%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegulation%20can%20make%20a%20difference%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20states%20have%20already%20implemented%20a%20patchwork%20of%20legal%20protections%20for%20victims%20of%20deepfakes%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Associated%20Press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20recent%20high-profile%20cases%20have%20upped%20the%20pressure%20on%20lawmakers%20to%20deter%20and%20punish%20the%20malicious%20use%20of%20AI%20and%20deepfakes.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Federal%20Communications%20Commission%20has%20banned%20AI-generated%20robocalls%20after%20hoax%20calls%20were%20made%20in%20the%20New%20Hampshire%20primaries%2C%20using%20an%20AI-generated%20voice%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-hampshire-democrats-received-deep-faked-calls-from-joe-biden-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esounded%20like%20Joe%20Biden%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20January%2C%20a%20bipartisan%20group%20of%20senators%20introduced%20a%20federal%20bill%20known%20as%20the%20DEFIANCE%20Act%20that%20would%20allow%20victims%20to%20sue%20those%20who%20create%20and%20distribute%20sexual%20deepfakes%20of%20them%2C%20making%20it%20a%20civil%20rather%20than%20criminal%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bill%20introduced%20last%20May%20by%20Rep.%20Joe%20Morelle%20to%20criminalize%20the%20sharing%20of%20deepfakes%20has%20not%20progressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20much%20of%20the%20new%20legislation%20is%20coming%20up%20against%20free%20speech%20proponents.%20The%20reason%2C%20according%20to%20Henry%20Ajder%2C%20is%20that%20some%20see%20the%20private%20creation%20of%20deepfakes%20as%20akin%20to%20a%20fantasy%20someone%20may%20have%20inside%20their%20head%20about%20a%20crush.%20If%20no%20one%20ever%20knows%20about%20the%20pornographic%20content%2C%20has%20anyone%20really%20been%20harmed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECriminal%20deterrents%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20had%20an%20effect%20on%20legislation%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20the%20Online%20Safety%20Act%20has%20made%20it%20illegal%20to%20distribute%20deepfake%20porn%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20to%20create%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20counterargument%20is%20that%20if%20you're%20creating%20this%20content%2C%20you're%20bringing%20into%20existence%20something%20that%20could%20be%20shared%20in%20a%20way%20that%20a%20fantasy%20can't%20really%20be%20shared%2C%26quot%3B%20Ajder%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20hard%20to%20prosecute%2C%20criminalizing%20deepfake%20porn%20is%20still%20an%20important%20deterrent%2C%20in%20his%20view.%20Some%20people%20are%20using%20AI%20tools%20to%20create%20content%20for%20their%20own%20private%20consumption%2C%20Ajder%20says.%20However%2C%20ensuring%20they%20realize%20this%20is%20criminal%20behavior%20is%20important%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20to%20deter%20those%20who%20might%20merely%20be%20curious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGovernments%20can%20also%20put%20pressure%20on%20search%20engine%20providers%2C%20AI-tool%20developers%2C%20and%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%20where%20content%20is%20distributed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20a%20deepfake%20porn%20scandal%20involving%20Bollywood%20actresses%20spurred%20the%20government%20to%20fasttrack%20legislation%20and%20pressure%20the%20big%20tech%20companies%20to%20prevent%20AI-generated%20content%20from%20being%20spread%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20not%20kid%20ourselves%20that%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20fully%20remove%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20admits%20Ajder.%20%26quot%3BThe%20best%20we%20can%20do%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20is%20introduce%20as%20much%20friction%20as%20possible%20so%20that%20you%20have%20to%20be%20incredibly%20intentional%20about%20trying%20to%20create%20this%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepfake-porn-huge-problem-ai-tools-help-stop-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708251721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c4f63d6fcb546d2d4d7b43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepfake-porn-huge-problem-ai-tools-help-stop-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tools%20designed%20to%20stop%20AI-generated%20deepfake%20porn%20targeting%20children%2C%20celebrities%2C%20and%20others%20include%20digital%20watermarks%2C%20poison%20pills%2C%20and%20better%20regulation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40insider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepfake-porn-huge-problem-ai-tools-help-stop-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20took%20trips%20on%20a%20year-old%20Norwegian%20Cruise%20Line%20ship%20and%20a%2025-year-old%20one.%20The%20differences%20show%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20industry.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Norwegian%20Sky%20next%20to%20the%20Norwegian%20Prima.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cf982bf533b039a884a8bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221655%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20newer%20Norwegian%20Prima%20(bottom)%20is%20larger%20with%20more%20grandiose%20amenities%20compared%20to%20the%20older%20Norwegian%20Sky%20(top).%3Cp%3ENorwegian%20Cruise%20Lines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20sailed%20on%20an%20older%20and%20newer%20ship%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-norwegian-cruise-line-new-1-billion-prima-cruise-ship-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENorwegian%20Cruise%20Line%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Sky%20and%20Prima.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20smaller%20Sky%20was%20basic%20compared%20to%20the%20Prima's%20dazzling%20%E2%80%94%20but%20more%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20activities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMass-market%20cruise%20lines%20have%20been%20building%20bigger%20ships%20with%20more%20pay-to-play%20amenities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20look%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-norwegian-cruise-line-new-1-billion-prima-cruise-ship-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENorwegian%20Cruise%20Line's%3C%2Fa%3E%20older%20and%20newer%20vessels%20will%20make%20you%20realize%20just%20how%20much%20bigger%2C%20bolder%2C%20and%20more%20irresistible%20cruise%20ships%20are%20becoming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDecades%20of%20modernization%20and%20astute%20profit-making%20strategies%20have%20pushed%20the%20mass-market%20cruise%20industry%20to%20transform%20its%20small%20floating%20hotels%20into%20giant%20resorts%20with%20amusement%20park-like%20amenities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20travelers%20have%20been%20loving%20this%20shift.%20Just%20look%20at%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froyal-caribbean-icon-of-the-seas-cruise-ship-review-photos-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIcon%20of%20the%20Seas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20what's%20now%20the%20world's%20largest%20cruise%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%209%2C950-person%20vessel's%20amenities%20%E2%80%94%20which%20include%20a%20six-slide%20waterpark%2C%20waterfall%2C%20and%20ice%20skating%20rink%20%E2%80%94%20could%20be%20one%20reason%20Icon%20has%20become%20its%20operator's%20most%20popular%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Icon%20of%20the%20Seas'%20outdoor%20decks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bc00dd7a3d27148876d4aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoyal%20Caribbean's%20g