0data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22447%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EYou'd%20probably%20envision%20something%20like%20the%20older%20Norwegian%20Sky%20when%20someone%20asks%20you%20to%20picture%20a%20typical%20cruise%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20all%20the%20basics%3A%20a%20casino%2C%20a%20buffet%2C%20bars%2C%20children's%20clubs%2C%20and%20a%20crowded%20pool%20deck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20compared%20to%20newer%20ships%2C%20it%20fell%20short%20of%20major%20%26quot%3Bwow%26quot%3B%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lobby%20of%20the%20Norwegian%20Sky%20with%20people%20around.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd14a443bb77284ba30721%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENorwegian%20Sky%20looked%20more%20like%20a%20dated%20beachside%20hotel.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20atrium%20was%20small%20and%20basic%2C%20the%20lounges%20lacked%20any%20razzle-dazzle%2C%20and%20the%20pool%20deck%20left%20much%20to%20be%20desired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20noticeably%2C%20it%20didn't%20have%20the%20grandiose%20amenities%20that%20are%20becoming%20more%20common%20on%20new%20ships%2C%20like%20the%20Prima.%20(Think%20water%20slides%2C%20flashy%20cocktail%20bars%2C%20and%20a%20go-kart%20race%20track.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20you%20read%20that%20right%3A%20go-karts.%20Good%20luck%20getting%20bored%20on%20the%20Norwegian%20Prima.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn-board%20amenities%20are%20getting%20flashier%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20expensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FaYvUJ%2F5%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Amenities%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5