https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fjapans-naked-men-festival-succumbs-to-population-ageing%2Famp_articleshow%2F107795931.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Says%20Congress%2C%20AAP%20%26quot%3BMutually%20Agreed%26quot%3B%20To%20Go%20Solo%20In%20Punjab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20had%20%26quot%3Bmutually%20agreed%26quot%3B%20to%20contest%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Punjab%20separately%20and%20there%20is%20no%20bad%20blood%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20over%20this%20issue%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20today%20visited%20Congress%20leader%20and%20renowned%20lawyer%20Abhishek%20Singhvi's%20home%20for%20lunch.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20on%20the%20decision%20by%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20Punjab%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20Punjab%2C%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20have%20mutually%20agreed%20to%20contest%20the%20polls%20separately.%20There%20is%20no%20hostility%20over%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tussle%20between%20Congress%20and%20AAP%2C%20rivals%20in%20Punjab%20but%20allies%20in%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20has%20made%20headlines%20for%20weeks%20now.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20AAP%20is%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%20to%20finalise%20seat-sharing%20in%20Delhi.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20an%20alliance%20in%20Delhi.%20We%20are%20discussing%20seat-sharing%20arrangements.%20The%20BJP%20will%20have%20it%20easy%20if%20there%20is%20no%20alliance%20(between%20Congress%20and%20AAP)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%20all%20seven%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20They%20had%20achieved%20the%20same%20feat%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20remark%20suggests%20that%20the%20INDIA%20allies%20have%20decide