d%20to%20announce%20the%20return%20of%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20to%20the%20squad%20after%20a%20brief%20absence%20due%20to%20a%20family%20emergency.%20Ashwin%20had%20to%20temporarily%20withdraw%20from%20the%20squad%20after%20Day%202%20of%20the%203rd%20Test%20in%20Rajkot%20to%20attend%20to%20a%20family%20emergency%2C%26quot%3B%20BCCI%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20R%20Ashwin%20and%20the%20team%20management%20are%20pleased%20to%20confirm%20that%20he%20will%20be%20back%20in%20action%20on%20Day%204%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20contribute%20towards%20the%20team's%20cause%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Test%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20also%20lauded%20every%20stakeholder%20for%20showing%20empathy%20during%20a%20critical%20phase%20for%20the%20star%20cricketer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20team%20management%2C%20players%2C%20media%20and%20fans%20have%20shown%20immense%20understanding%20and%20empathy%2C%20acknowledging%20the%20importance%20of%20family%20as%20a%20priority.%20The%20team%20and%20its%20supporters%20have%20stood%20united%20in%20support%20of%20Ashwin%20during%20this%20challenging%20period%2C%20and%20the%20management%20is%20delighted%20to%20welcome%20him%20back%20to%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAshwin%20and%20his%20family%20kindly%20request%20privacy%20as%20they%20navigate%20through%20these%20challenging%20times.%26quot%3B%20Former%20India%20wicketkeeper-batter%20Dinesh%20Karthik%20had%20hinted%20about%20Ashwin's%20imminent%20return%20on-air%20while%20commentating%20for%20the%20host%20broadcaster%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20proceedings%20on%20day%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708248420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fknpevekg_ravichandra