tion%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20in%20the%20original%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20on%20the%20section%20of%20fundamental%20rights%2C%20the%20picture%20of%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%2C%20Mother%20Sita%20and%20Lakshman%20ji%20after%20returning%20to%20Ayodhya%20after%20the%20victory%20is%20a%20proof%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%20is%20the%20source%20of%20inspiration%20for%20the%20fundamental%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resolution%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20idea%20of%20'Ram%20Rajya'%20was%20also%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Bapu%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20used%20to%20say%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20'Ram%20Rajya'%20is%20the%20idea%20of%20true%20democracy.%20Following%20the%20ideals%20of%20Lord%20Shri%20Ram%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20has%20implemented%20the%20spirit%20of%20'Ram%20Rajya'%20in%20the%20true%20sense%20by%20establishing%20good%20governance%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20values%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20instilled%20in%20his%20words%20and%20thoughts%20are%20the%20inspiration%20for%20'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas%2C'%20and%20the%20basis%20of%20'Sabka%20Vishwas%2C%20Sabka%20Prayas'%2C%20the%20resolution%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20India's%20unity%20and%20solidarity%20have%20received%20the%20power%20of%20public%20participation.%20He%20has%20raised%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20nation%20with%20his%20policies%20and%20leadership.%20Indian%20cultural%2C%20spiritual%20and%20historical%20pride%20has%20been%20restored%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20convention%20congratulates%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20for%20making%20the%20shared%20power%20of%20heritage%20and%20development%20the%20identity%20of%20new%20India%20through%20his%20determined%20efforts%20and%20thanks%20the%20pri