%20between%20rival%20political%20parties%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election.%20But%20scratch%20the%20surface%20and%20what%20emerges%20is%20a%20baffling%20tale%20of%20Shahjahan's%20meteoric%20rise%20to%20power%20and%20how%20he%20managed%20to%20turn%20this%20island%20into%20his%20fiefdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Beginning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahjahan's%20journey%20to%20become%20Sandeshkhali's%20strongman%20began%20well%20before%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20came%20to%20power.%20Not%20much%20is%20known%20about%20his%20educational%20background.%20In%20his%20nomination%20papers%20for%20the%20panchayat%20polls%2C%20the%20column%20of%20educational%20qualifications%20was%20vacant.%20Local%20media%20reports%20say%20that%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20Shahjahan%20would%20be%20seen%20on%20the%20sidestep%20of%20cars%20playing%20between%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20neighbouring%20Sarberia%2C%20calling%20out%20to%20passengers%20and%20collecting%20fare%20from%20them.%20His%20maternal%20uncle%2C%20Moslem%20Sheikh%2C%20was%20a%20local%20CPM%20leader%20and%20the%20panchayat%20chief.%20Sheikh%20gave%20Shahjahan%20his%20first%20breakthrough%2C%20and%20the%20ambitious%20nephew%20started%20looking%20after%20the%20local%20fish%20trade.%20He%20was%20no%20leader%2C%20yet%2C%20and%20largely%20worked%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20his%20uncle%2C%20helping%20him%20out%20during%20elections%20and%20keeping%20in%20touch%20with%20local%20party%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20assets%2C%20however%2C%20started%20growing%20and%20that%20did%20not%20go%20unnoticed.%20It%20is%20around%20this%20time%20that%20Shahjahan%20started%20carving%20out%20his%20identity.%20He%20helped%20out%20local%20residents%20during%20crisis.%20Whether%20it%20is%20arranging%20funds%20for%20a%20wedding%20or%20helping%20out%20parents%20struggling%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20children's%20education%2C%20Shahjahan%20was%20the%20go-to%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%202010%2C%20he%20sensed%20the%20wind%20of%20change%20blowing%20against%20the%20ruling%20CPM%2C%20even%20before%20his%20uncle%20did.%20Local%20media%20reports%20said%20Shahjahan%20gradually%20started%20distancing%20himself%20from%20CPM%20as%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20Trinamool%20Congress%20gained%20ground%20ahead%20of%20the%202011%20polls.%20Shahjahan's%20calculation%20proved%20right%20when%20the%2034-year%20rule%20of%20the%20Left%20ended%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trinamool%20leader%20Jyotipriya%20Mallick%2C%20now%20in%20jail%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%2C%20was%20watching%20the%20ambitious%20nephew.%20Mallick%2C%20local%20reports%20said%2C%20planned%20to%20deal%20a%20fatal%20blow%20to%20the%20CPM%20by%20using%20Shahjahan%20to%20counter%20his%20uncle%20Moslem%20Sheikh's%20influence.%20In%202013%2C%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20joined%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%20The%20tide%20had%20turned%20and%20the%20nephew%20and%20trumped%20his%20uncle.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20Moslem%20Sheikh%20was%20forced%20to%20join%20Trinamool%20a%20few%20years%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Mountain%20Of%20Wealth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20palatial%20homes%2C%20coloured%20white%2C%20blue%20and%20yellow%2C%20tower%20over%20Akunjipara%20More%20near%20Sandeshkali.%20The%20blue%20and%20white%20homes%20are%20occupied%20by%20Shahjahan's%20relatives.%20The%2050-year-old%20strongman%20lived%20in%20the%20yellow%20before%20he%20fled%20ahead%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20raid.%20Documents%20submitted%20for%20panchayat%20polls%20stated%20Shahjahan%20owns%2017%20cars%2C%2043%20bighas%20of%20land%20--%20about%2023%20acres%20--%20and%20jewellery%20worth%20over%20Rs%202%20crore.%20His%20bank%20balance%20was%20nearly%20Rs%202%20crore.%20The%20strongman%20mentioned%20his%20occupation%20as%20'business'%20and%20his%20annual%20income%20was%20shown%20as%20nearly%20Rs%2020%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20residents%2C%20however%2C%20claim%20that%20his%20actual%20property%20is%20much%20more.%20But%20where%20was%20the%20money%20coming%20from%3F%20Local%20leaders%20say%20he%20owned%20two%20brick%20kilns%20and%20was%20regularly%20seen%20there.%20That%20was%20not%20all.%20Shahjahan's%20aides%20collected%20a%20cut%20from%20every%20fish%20trader%20in%20the%20area.%20Firearms%20tucked%20into%20their%20belts%2C%20his%20men%20would%20go%20from%20one%20fish%20grower%20to%20another%2C%20collecting%20the%20strongman's%20%26quot%3Bfee%26quot%3B%20every%20month%2C%20according%20to%20local%20reports.%20Such%20was%20his%20terror%20in%20the%20area%20that%20no%20one%20dared%20to%20oppose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllegations%20of%20Land%20Grab%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20agricultural%20production%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20saw%20a%20swift%20decline%20and%20fish%20cultivation%20an%20exponential%20growth.%20Behind%20this%20was%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%20Local%20residents%20recount%20the%20strongman's%20oft-repeated%20expression%3A%20nona%20jole%20sona%20fole%20(Gold%20grows%20in%20saline%20water).%20His%20ways%20to%20%26quot%3Bgrow%20gold%26quot%3B%2C%20however%2C%20have%20drawn%20serious%20allegations%20of%20land%20grab.%20Several%20farmers%20have%20narrated%20to%20NDTV%20how%20Shahjahan%20took%20control%20of%20land.%20His%20men%20would%20break%20embankments%20to%20channel%20saline%20water%20into%20agricultural%20land.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20inundated%20our%20land%20with%20saline%20water%20so%20that%20we%20cannot%20grow%20crops%20here.%20(Shahjahan's%20aides)%20Uttam%20Sardar%20and%20Shibu%20Hazra%20did%20this.%20Now%20they%20are%20rearing%20lobsters%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20local%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20farmer%20alleged%20that%20they%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20rear%20fish.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20will%20we%20go%20into%20fish%20farming%20when%20we%20have%20this%20land%3F%20We%20used%20to%20grow%20rice%20and%20live%20off%20it.%20We%20grew%20crops%20and%20fed%20ourselves.%20Fish%20and%20rice%20sufficed.%20Now%2C%20everything%20has%20stopped.%20There%20is%20no%20vegetable%20and%20there%20is%20no%20crop.%20Our%20cows%20don't%20have%20anything%20to%20eat%20as%20there%20is%20no%20grass.%20What%20will%20we%20do%3F%20We%20are%20dying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtest%2C%20the%20local%20farmers%20said%2C%20would%20attract%20a%20hefty%20penalty.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20protesting%20now%20because%20we%20cannot%20take%20it%20anymore.%20They%20pick%20us%20up%20and%20beat%20us.%20This%20is%20the%20situation.%20We%20cannot%20sleep%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20farmer%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20identified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20objective%20was%20simple%20--%20turn%20land%20into%20fish%20farms%20and%20reap%20the%20profits.%20Every%20piece%20of%20land%2C%20including%20a%20footfall%20field%20named%20after%20him%2C%20was%20on%20Shahjahan's%20radar%20as%20he%20went%20on%20building%20his%20fiefdom%2C%20local%20residents%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Extortion%20Network%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20residents%20allege%20that%20they%20would%20get%20only%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20the%20money%20that%20came%20into%20their%20accounts%20under%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government.%20This%20also%20applied%20to%20payments%20for%20work%20under%20MGNREGA%2C%20the%20rural%20job%20guarantee%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20get%20maybe%20Rs%20500.%20They%20did%20not%20give%20us%20the%20rest%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20local%20resident%20said%2C%20targeting%20Shahjahan's%20aides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShahjahan's%20men%20would%20pick%20us%20up%20from%20our%20home.%20We%20would%20be%20made%20to%20withdraw%20the%20money%20and%20give%20it%20to%20them.%20They%20would%20hand%20us%20Rs%20500.%20'Take%20this%2C%20we%20won't%20give%20you%20the%20rest'%2C%20they%20said%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%20A%20protest%20would%20invite%20a%20thrashing%2C%20they%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20group%20of%20men%20said%20payment%20for%20building%20roads%20or%20digging%20ponds%20would%20also%20be%20snatched%20by%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20men.%20%26quot%3BThis%20road%20has%20been%20built%2C%20but%20we%20have%20not%20been%20paid.%20When%20we%20dug%20a%20pond%2C%20we%20did%20not%20get%20money%20for%20it.%20Not%20a%20single%20rupee.%20If%20we%20said%20anything%2C%20they%20would%20pick%20us%20up%20and%20beat%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20Is%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sandeshkhali%20strongman%20has%20been%20missing%20since%20a%20team%20of%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officials%20came%20under%20a%20mob%20attack%20when%20they%20went%20to%20raid%20his%20home%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20in%20January.%20The%20recent%20allegations%20of%20harassment%20by%20women%20have%20raised%20a%20political%20storm%20and%20prompted%20the%20state%20police%20to%20crack%20down.%20Shahjahan's%20aides%20Shibu%20Hazra%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20but%20he%20is%20still%20on%20the%20run.%20State%20police%20chief%20Rajeev%20Kumar%20said%20a%2010-member%20committee%20is%20investigating%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20total%20of%2017%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20cop%20said%20state%20police%20is%20not%20trying%20to%20hide%20anything%20and%20appealed%20to%20villagers%20to%20come%20forward%20with%20their%20complaints.%20The%20police%20are%20also%20organising%20camps%20in%20the%20area%20to%20take%20complaints%20of%20land%20grab%20and%20extortion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20has%20registered%20a%20complaint%20of%20rape.%20Basirhat%20police%20chief%20HM%20Rehman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20complaints%20received%20by%20us%20from%20the%20police%20team%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20as%20well%20as%20the%20police%20station%20did%20not%20mention%20any%20cases%20of%20rape.%20However%2C%20in%20court%2C%20one%20woman%20has%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20of%20rape.%20The%20police%20will%20take%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%2C%20however%2C%20said%20they%20have%20not%20received%20any%20complaint%20specifically%20naming%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh.%C2%A0The%20main%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20of%20shielding%20the%20strongman%20and%20called%20for%20strict%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708243560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fat1giiog_sheikh-shahjahan_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-whos-sheikh-shahjahan-trinamool-strongman-at-centre-of-sandeshkali-row-5080238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Till%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20Sandeshkhali%20island%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20was%20just%20a%20dot%20on%20the%20map.%20But%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20this%20nondescript%20island%20has%20made%20national%20headlines%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-whos-sheikh-shahjahan-trinamool-strongman-at-centre-of-sandeshkali-row-5080238%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-whos-sheikh-shahjahan-trinamool-strongman-at-centre-of-sandeshkali-row-5080238%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsheikh-shahjahan-sandeshkhali-whos-sheikh-shahjahan-trinamool-strongman-at-centre-of-sandeshkali-row-5080238%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TISS%20Administration%20Tried%20to%20Stop%20a%20Lecture%20by%20Bezwada%20Wilson%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fbezwada-wilson.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20(TISS)%20in%20Mumbai%20reportedly%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20halt%20an%20online%20lecture%20organised%20by%20a%20student%20body%2C%20featuring%20Magsaysay%20award%20winner%20and%20rights%20activist%20Bezwada%20Wilson.%20This%20comes%20a%20year%20after%20their%20previous%20effort%20to%20disrupt%20a%20similar%20lecture%20by%20researcher%20and%20human%20rights%20activist%20Harsh%20Mander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fliberal-bastion-bid-to-gag-activist-bezwada-wilsons-lecture-at-tata-institute-of-social-sciences%2Fcid%2F2001244%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Students%20Organising%20Committee%2C%20an%20independent%20forum%20of%20TISS%20students%2C%20had%20informed%20the%20administration%20in%20December%202023%20about%20the%20proposed%20lecture%20by%20Wilson%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CBhagat%20Singh%20Memorial%20Lecture%E2%80%9D%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20the%20institute%20issued%20an%20order%20a%20few%20weeks%20later%20that%20no%20programmes%20by%20students%20would%20be%20allowed%20till%20new%20guidelines%20were%20notified%20%E2%80%93%20though%20the%20date%20for%20the%20new%20guidelines%20was%20unspecified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Friday%2C%20TISS%20authorities%20released%20a%20notice%20that%20the%20event%20was%20unauthorised.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20it%20has%20come%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20this%20Institute%20that%20some%20unauthorised%20student%20bodies%2F%20organisation%20claiming%20itself%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20TISS%20is%20going%20to%20organise%20an%20event%20titled%20as%20%E2%80%98Bhagat%20Singh%20Memorial%20Lecture%E2%80%99%20on%2017th%20February%2C%202024%20via%20online%2F%20offline%20mode%20from%2004%3A00%20p.m.%20onwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20regard%2C%20all%20the%20students%2C%20faculties%2C%20staff%20of%20the%20Institute%20and%20public%20at%20large%20are%20hereby%20informed%20that%20organising%20of%20such%20event%20has%20not%20been%20permitted%20by%20this%20Institute%20by%20any%20means%20and%20it%20has%20no%20relation%20with%20TISS.%20Hence%2C%20in%20view%20of%20above%2C%20all%20the%20concern%20is%20hereby%20requested%20to%20not%20to%20associate%20the%20above%20events%20with%20TISS%20in%20any%20capacity%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20event%20went%20ahead%20over%20Zoom%2C%20with%20Wilson%2C%20an%20activist%20against%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20manual%20scavenging%2C%20giving%20a%20lecture%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20%E2%80%9CHuman%20rights%20and%20constitutional%20values%20in%20contemporary%20times%3A%20Role%20of%20university%20and%20public%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20student%2C%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20that%20since%20the%20institute%20has%20yet%20to%20notify%20the%20new%20guidelines%2C%20the%20event%20could%20not%20be%20illegal%20and%20therefore%20it%20went%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20name%20of%20issuing%20new%20guidelines%2C%20the%20institute%20has%20been%20creating%20hurdles%20before%20students%E2%80%99%20activities.%20The%20students%20are%20a%20major%20stakeholder%20and%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20institute.%20Efforts%20to%20curb%20their%20voice%20are%20undemocratic%20and%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20another%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20report%2C%20citing%20three%20students%2C%20said%20TISS%20students%20had%20been%20organising%20the%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Memorial%20lecture%20since%202018.%20Earlier%20it%20was%20held%20in%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20amphitheatre%2C%20but%20it%20was%20shifted%20online%20in%202021%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202023%2C%20TISS%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.