F2024%2F02%2FSaltburn.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235915194%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20being%20significantly%20hit%20by%20the%20WGA%20and%20SAG-AFTRA%20strikes%20in%202023%2C%20U.K.%20film%20studios%20and%20production%20facilities%20are%20looking%20to%20pick%20back%20up%20where%20they%20left%20off%20after%20a%20record-breaking%20year%20for%20film%20and%20high-end%20television%20production%20spend%20in%202022.%20When%20asked%20what%20the%20industry%20can%20expect%20in%20terms%20of%20business%20in%20the%20year%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Leo%20Barraclough%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fbritish-production-sector-2-1235915194%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fbritish-production-sector-2-1235915194%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fbritish-production-sector-2-1235915194%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20Union%20Govt%20Took%20a%20Big%20Step%20Towards%20NPR%2C%20NRC%20in%202015%20Without%20Informed%20Consent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F22120239%2FMANUU.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ECitizen%E2%80%99s%20activism%20through%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20(RTI)%20has%20revealed%20how%2C%20a%20giant%20step%20towards%20NPR%20and%20NRC%20was%20taken%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20when%20the%20information%20contained%20in%20the%20Aadhaar%20database%20was%20linked%20with%20the%20NPR%20database%20in%202015.%20While%20the%20only%20legal%20way%20of%20linking%20the%20two%20databases%20is%20by%20acquiring%C2%A0%3Cb%3Einformed%20consent%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0from%20every%20resident%20through%20a%20public%20exercise%20similar%20to%20the%20Census%2C%20which%20means%20through%20a%20public%20exercise%20conducted%20by%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20(RGI)%2C%20investigations%20reveal%20that%20the%20exercise%20did%20not%20have%20any%20provision%20to%20collect%C2%A0%3Ci%3Eany%20informed%20consent%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3Efor%20this%20linkage%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0This%20presentation%20below%2C%20exclusively%20available%20on%20CJP%20reveals%20that%20this%20apparently%20illegal%20action%20makes%20the%20NPR%20an%20even%20greater%20threat%20to%20the%20common%20people%20than%20what%20was%20previously%20thought.%20The%20involved%20citizens%20in%20and%20around%20Metiabruz%20Kolkata%20are%20close%20collaborators%20with%C2%A0%3Ci%3ECitizens%20for%20Justice%20and%20Peace%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E(cjp.org.in)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nationwide%20movement%20against%20the%20National%20Population%20Register%20(NPR)%20and%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%2C%20which%20was%20triggered%20by%20passing%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Bill%20(CAB)%2C%20came%20to%20an%20abrupt%20halt%20in%202020%20after%20the%20outbreak%20of%20Covid-19%2C%20the%20subsequent%20lockdown%20imposed%20by%20the%20government%20and%20the%20repression%20unleashed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20and%20UP%20police%20on%20the%20young%20leadership%20that%20was%20protesting%20the%20issue.%20CJP%20had%20taken%20the%20lead%20then%20as%20among%20the%20main%20civil%20and%20legal%20rights%20organisation%20to%20create%20public%20advocacy%20and%20awareness%20of%20the%20dangers%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%202003%20amendment%20to%20the%20Citizenship%20Rules%20(Indian%20Citizenship%20Act%2C%202003)%20that%20present%20the%20danger%20of%20bureaucratic%20profiling%20and%20exclusion%20of%20large%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20citizenry%2C%20especially%20unlettered%20and%20marginalized%20Indians.%20CJP%E2%80%99s%20experience%20of%20working%20over%206%20years%20in%20Assam%20(since%202017)%20has%20ensured%20a%20deep%2C%20nuanced%20and%20thorough%20knowledge%20of%20how%20the%20on-ground%20implications%20of%20a%20bureaucracy%20driven%20documentary%20%E2%80%9Ctest%E2%80%9D%20for%20citizens%20means%20denial%20of%20citizenship%20rights%2C%20alienation%20of%20all%20rights%20to%20exist%20in%20terms%20of%20access%20to%20institutions%20and%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20impoverishment%20and%20physical%20and%20mental%20discriminations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EToday%2C%202024%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vibrant%20call%20of%20the%20nationwide%20movement%20was%C2%A0%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3EKagaj%20Nehi%20Dikhayenge%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%2C%20i.e.%2C%20we%20shall%20not%20show%20any%20document%20had%20gathered%20momentum%20and%20was%20thus%20silenced.%20CJP%E2%80%99s%20investigation%20has%20shown%20how%2C%20the%20government%20has%20already%20started%20a%20process%20of%20NPR-NRC%20via%20an%20indirect%20another%20route%20which%20required%20no%20documentary%20evidence%20from%20the%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20a%20group%20in%20Metiabruz%2C%20a%20part%20of%20Kolkata%20district%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20close%20collaborators%20with%20CJP%2C%20re-started%20their%20endeavour%20to%20build%20up%20an%20agitation%20to%20resist%20NPR-NRC-CAA.%20They%20opposed%20all%20amendments%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%201955%2C%20which%20vitiated%20our%20constitutional%20right%20to%20citizenship%20by%20birth.%20In%202023%20they%20were%20surprised%20to%20discover%20that%20the%C2%A0%3Ci%3EAnnual%20Report%202021-22%20of%20MHA%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0declared%20(in%20section%2015.41%20of%20NPR)%20that%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202015%2C%20a%20few%20fields%20such%20as%20Name%2C%20Gender%2C%20Date%20and%20Place%20of%20Birth%2C%20Place%20of%20Residence%20and%20Father%E2%80%99s%20and%20Mother%E2%80%99s%20name%20were%20updated%20and%20Aadhaar%2C%20Mobile%20and%20Ration%20Card%20Numbers%20were%20collected%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20But%20neither%20did%20they%20witness%20any%20such%20exercise%20being%20carried%20out%20in%20their%20locality%20from%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20(RGI)%2C%20nor%20did%20any%20enumerator%20come%20to%20them%20for%20updating%20NPR%20and%20for%20collecting%20Aadhaar%20Number%20in%202015-16.%20So%2C%20this%20event%20led%20them%20to%20file%20a%20series%20of%20RTIs%2C%20First%20Appeals%20and%20Second%20Appeals%20to%20the%20concerned%20government%20authorities%20to%20verify%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20NPR%20process%20starting%20from%202010.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConnecting%20the%20dots%20of%20publicly%20available%20information%20with%20the%20information%20obtained%20through%20RTI%20brings%20out%20a%20compelling%20and%20frightening%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20appears%20that%20a%20giant%20step%20towards%20NPR%20and%20NRC%20was%20taken%20quietly%20when%20information%20belonging%20to%20the%20Aadhaar%20database%20was%20linked%20with%20the%20NPR%20database.%20The%20only%20legal%20way%20of%20linking%20the%20two%20databases%20is%20by%20acquiring%C2%A0%3Cb%3Einformed%20consent%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0from%20every%20resident%20through%20an%20exercise%20similar%20to%20the%20Census.%20That%20exercise%20would%20have%20surely%20evoked%20public%20outrage%20similar%20to%20what%20had%20been%20witnessed%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20passing%20of%20CAA%2FCAB.%20However%2C%20it%20seems%20from%20the%20replies%20to%20the%20series%20of%20RTI%20queries%20that%20the%20linking%20was%20done%C2%A0%3Ci%3Ewithout%20any%20informed%20consent.%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0This%20apparently%20illegal%20action%20makes%20the%20NPR%20an%20even%20greater%20threat%20to%20the%20common%20people%20than%20what%20was%20previously%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20developments%20pose%20a%20clear%20and%20present%20danger%20of%20no%20less%20magnitude%20than%20what%20triggered%20the%20CAA-%20NPR-NRC%20movement%2C%20though%20there%20is%20no%20conspicuous%20symbol%20of%20that%20danger%20visible%20to%20the%20public.%20Citizens%20have%20to%20come%20together%20and%20prevent%20governmental%20overreach%20and%20harassment%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcjp.org.in%2Fcjp-exclusive-how-the-union-of-india-took-a-giant-step-towards-both-npr-nrc-in-2015-without-informed-consent%2F%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Citizens%20for%20Justice%20and%20Peace%20website.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708240535000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F22120239%2FMANUU.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhow-the-union-govt-took-a-big-step-towards-npr-nrc-in-2015-without-informed-consent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20step%20was%20taken%20when%20information%20contained%20in%20the%20Aadhaar%20database%20was%20linked%20with%20the%20NPR%20database%20without%20informed%20consent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhow-the-union-govt-took-a-big-step-towards-npr-nrc-in-2015-without-informed-consent%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shilpa's%20warm%20gesture%20towards%20disabled%20fan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708240362000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107792760%2Cimgsize-41506.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshilpa-shettys-heartwarming-gesture-towards-disabled-fans-steals-the-spotlight%2Farticleshow%2F107792770.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107792770.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EReturning%20from%20a%20family%20vacation%20in%20Singapore%20on%20Saturday%2C%20February%2017%2C%20Bollywood's%20influential%20couple%20Shilpa%20Shetty%20and%20Raj%20Kundra%2C%20accompanied%20by%20their%20children%20Viaan%20and%20Samisha%2C%20garnered%20attention%20with%20their%20casual%20airport%20ap