and%20social%20unrest%20left%20by%20leaders%20who%20have%20held%20power%20for%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fyouth-led-activism-sweeps-across-africa-eswatinis-struggle-for-change-as-protesters-sought-to-oust-king-mswati-iii%2Farticleshow%2F107791800.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fyouth-led-activism-sweeps-across-africa-eswatinis-struggle-for-change-as-protesters-sought-to-oust-king-mswati-iii%2Famp_articleshow%2F107791800.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fyouth-led-activism-sweeps-across-africa-eswatinis-struggle-for-change-as-protesters-sought-to-oust-king-mswati-iii%2Famp_articleshow%2F107791800.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Japan's%20'Naked%20Men'%20Festival%20Succumbs%20To%20Population%20Ageing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20steam%20of%20sweat%20rose%20as%20hundreds%20of%20naked%20men%20tussled%20over%20a%20bag%20of%20wooden%20talismans%2C%20performing%20a%20dramatic%20end%20to%20a%20thousand-year-old%20ritual%20in%20Japan%20that%20took%20place%20for%20the%20last%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20passionate%20chants%20of%20%26quot%3Bjasso%2C%20joyasa%26quot%3B%20(meaning%20%26quot%3Bevil%2C%20be%20gone%26quot%3B)%20echoed%20through%20a%20ceder%20forest%20of%20the%20northern%20Japan's%20Iwate%20region%2C%20where%20the%20secluded%20Kokuseki%20Temple%20has%20decided%20to%20end%20the%20popular%20annual%20rite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOrganising%20the%20event%2C%20which%20draws%20hundreds%20of%20participants%20and%20thousands%20of%20tourists%20every%20year%2C%20has%20become%20a%20heavy%20burden%20for%20the%20ageing%20local%20faithful%2C%20who%20find%20it%20hard%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20rigours%20of%20the%20ritual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BSominsai%26quot%3B%20festival%2C%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20strangest%20festivals%20in%20Japan%2C%20is%20the%20latest%20tradition%20impacted%20by%20the%20country's%20ageing%20population%20crisis%20that%20has%20hit%20rural%20communities%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20organise%20a%20festival%20of%20this%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Daigo%20Fujinami%2C%20a%20resident%20monk%20of%20the%20temple%20that%20opened%20in%20729.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20see%20what%20happened%20today%20--so%20many%20people%20are%20here%20and%20it's%20all%20exciting.%20But%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20there%20are%20many%20rituals%20and%20so%20much%20work%20that%20have%20to%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20be%20blind%20to%20the%20difficult%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgeing%20population%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20society%20has%20aged%20more%20rapidly%20than%20most%20other%20countries'.%20The%20trend%20has%20forced%20countless%20schools%2C%20shops%20and%20services%20to%20close%2C%20particularly%20in%20small%20or%20rural%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKokuseki%20Temple's%20Sominsai%20festival%20used%20to%20take%20place%20from%20the%20seventh%20day%20of%20Lunar%20New%20Year%20through%20to%20the%20following%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%20it%20was%20scaled%20down%20to%20prayer%20ceremonies%20and%20smaller%20rituals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20festival%20was%20a%20shortened%20version%2C%20ending%20around%2011%3A00%20pm%2C%20but%20it%20drew%20the%20biggest%20crowd%20in%20recent%20memory%2C%20local%20residents%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20set%2C%20men%20in%20white%20loincloths%20came%20to%20the%20mountainous%20temple%2C%20bathed%20in%20a%20creek%20and%20marched%20around%20temple's%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20clenched%20their%20fists%20against%20the%20chill%20of%20a%20winter%20breeze%2C%20all%20the%20while%20chanting%20%26quot%3Bjasso%20joyasa%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20held%20small%20cameras%20to%20record%20their%20experience%2C%20while%20dozens%20of%20television%20crews%20followed%20the%20men%20through%20the%20temple's%20stone%20steps%20and%20dirt%20pathways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20festival%20reached%20its%20climax%2C%20hundreds%20of%20men%20packed%20inside%20the%20wooden%20temple%20shouting%2C%20chanting%20and%20aggressively%20jostling%20over%20a%20bag%20of%20talismans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanging%20norms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToshiaki%20Kikuchi%2C%20a%20local%20resident%20who%20claimed%20the%20talismans%20and%20who%20helped%20organise%20the%20festival%20for%20years%2C%20said%20he%20hoped%20the%20ritual%20will%20return%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20under%20a%20different%20format%2C%20I%20hope%20to%20maintain%20this%20tradition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20after%20the%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20things%20that%20you%20can%20appreciate%20only%20if%20you%20take%20part.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20participants%20and%20visitors%20voiced%20both%20sadness%20and%20understanding%20about%20the%20festival's%20ending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20last%20of%20this%20great%20festival%20that%20has%20lasted%201%2C000%20years.%20I%20really%20wanted%20to%20participate%20in%20this%20festival%2C%26quot%3B%20Yasuo%20Nishimura%2C%2049%2C%20a%20caregiver%20from%20Osaka%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20temples%20across%20Japan%20continue%20to%20host%20similar%20festivals%20where%20men%20wear%20loincloths%20and%20bathe%20in%20freezing%20water%20or%20fight%20over%20talismans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20festivals%20are%20adjusting%20their%20rules%20in%20line%20with%20changing%20democraphics%20and%20social%20norms%20so%20that%20they%20can%20continue%20to%20exist%20--%20such%20as%20letting%20women%20take%20part%20in%20previously%20male-only%20ceremonies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20next%20year%2C%20Kokuseki%20Temple%20will%20replace%20the%20festival%20with%20prayer%20ceremonies%20and%20other%20ways%20to%20continue%20its%20spiritual%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJapan%20is%20facing%20a%20falling%20birthrate%2C%20ageing%20population%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20young%20people%20to%20continue%20various%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Nishimura%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPerhaps%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20continue%20the%20same%20way%20as%20in%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708238820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-02%2F175i8ujs_hadaka-matsuri_625x300_17_February_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapans-naked-men-festival-succumbs-to-population-ageing-5080012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20steam%20of%20sweat%20rose%20as%20hundreds%20of%20naked%20men%20tussled%20over%20a%20bag%20of%20wooden%20talismans%2C%20performing%20a%20dramatic%20end%20to%20a%20thousand-year-old%20ritual%20in%20Japan%20that%20took%20place%20for%20the%20last%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapans-naked-men-festival-succumbs-to-population-ageing-5080012%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapans-naked-men-festival-succumbs-to-population-ageing-5080012%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjapans-naked-men-festival-succumbs-to-population-ageing-5080012%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20Thailand%20PM%20and%20Manchester%20City%20owner%20freed%20from%20detention%20after%20six%20months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17082