ruary_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fviral-video-movie-style-theft-from-mini-truck-on-meghalaya-highway-5079805%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20thieves%20were%20seen%20in%20a%20viral%20video%20stealing%20from%20a%20moving%20mini-truck%20in%20Meghalaya%20in%20a%20daring%20act%20that%20resembled%20a%20movie%20scene.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fviral-video-movie-style-theft-from-mini-truck-on-meghalaya-highway-5079805%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fviral-video-movie-style-theft-from-mini-truck-on-meghalaya-highway-5079805%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fviral-video-movie-style-theft-from-mini-truck-on-meghalaya-highway-5079805%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Jaiswal%2C%20England%20Star's%20Bizarre%20%26quot%3BWe%20Should%20Take%20Some%20Credit%26quot%3B%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEngland's%20Ben%20Duckett%20on%20Saturday%20called%20India's%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuperstar%20in%20the%20making%26quot%3B%20but%20said%20his%20side%20deserves%20credit%20for%20inspiring%20players%20in%20the%20opposition%20camp%20to%20bat%20aggressively%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20Jaiswal%20dished%20out%20his%20own%20version%20of%20England's%20much%20talked-about%20'Bazball'%20approach%20of%20run-making%20in%20Test%20cricket%2C%20cracking%20nine%20fours%20and%20five%20sixes%20in%20his%20133-ball%20104%20before%20retiring%20hurt%20due%20to%20back%20spasms.%20The%20Indian%20opener%20shifted%20gears%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20in%20the%20final%20session.%20Having%20reached%2035%20off%2073%20balls%2C%20he%20peppered%20the%20field%20with%20powerful%20strokes%20to%20bring%20up%20his%20second%20century%20of%20the%20series%20and%20third%20overall%20in%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20players%20from%20the%20opposition%20playing%20like%20that%2C%20it%20almost%20feels%20like%20we%20should%20take%20some%20credit%20that%20they're%20playing%20differently%20than%20how%20other%20people%20play%20Test%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Duckett%20told%20the%20media%20during%20a%20press%20conference%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20saw%20it%20a%20bit%20in%20the%20summer%20and%20it's%20quite%20exciting%20to%20see%20other%20players%20and%20other%20teams%20are%20also%20playing%20that%20aggressive%20style%20of%20cricket.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BHe%20looks%20like%20a%20superstar%20in%20the%20making%2C%20unfortunately%20he's%20in%20some%20very%20good%20form%20at%20the%20moment.%20He's%20due%20a%20couple%20of%20low%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20Duckett%20said%20while%20making%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20remark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuckett%2C%20however%2C%20defended%20former%20England%20captain%20and%20senior%20batter%20Joe%20Root%2C%20whose%20reverse-ramp%20shot%20off%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20resulted%20in%20his%20dismissal%2C%20which%20also%20sparked%20a%20collapse%20of%20sorts%20in%20the%20visiting%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20be%20interested%20to%20know%20if%20those%20people%20were%20against%20it%20when%20he%20was%20doing%20it%20to%20Pat%20Cummins%20and%20hitting%20him%20for%20six%20in%20the%20summer%2C%26quot%3B%20Duckett%20shot%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20no%20words%20really%20for%20it.%20It's%20the%20same%20as%20me%20playing%20a%20reverse%20sweep%20and%20getting%20caught%20at%20point.%20Options%20are%20practised%20and%20that%20shot%20has%20been%20very%20successful%20for%20him%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20so%20next%20time%20it%20may%20go%20over%20the%20slips%2C%26quot%3B%20Duckett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diminutive%20opener%2C%20who%20nearly%20broke%20the%20English%20record%20for%20fastest%20Test%20century%20on%20Day%20Two%2C%20finished%20on%20153%20off%20151%20balls%20with%2023%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20resuming%20on%20133%2C%20Duckett%20could%20not%20add%20more%20to%20his%20overnight%20total%20before%20being%20dismissed%20by%20Kuldeep%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuckett%20said%20India%20had%20better%20plans%20in%20place%20for%20Day%20Three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20one%20of%20those%20days%20when%20I%20feel%20we%20have%20to%20give%20credit%20to%20India.%20This%20morning%20they%20were%20very%20good%20and%20they%20didn't%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20score%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20their%20plans%20were%20a%20lot%20better%20than%20maybe%20last%20night%20and%20unfortunately%20we%20just%20kept%20on%20losing%20wickets%20at%20the%20wrong%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20ball%2C%20I%20didn't%20think%20we%20bowled%20badly%20at%20all%20and%20Jaiswal%20has%20played%20another%20incredible%20innings%20there.%20He%20looks%20an%20amazing%20player%2C%26quot%3B%20Duckett%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuckett%20credited%20his%20work%20behind%20the%20scenes%20for%20flourishing%20against%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20when%20compared%20to%20his%20previous%20face-off%20with%20the%20ace%20Indian%20spinner%20as%20well%20as%20Kuldeep%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20long%20time%20ago%20and%20I%20was%20very%20young%20then.%20It's%20obviously%20a%20very%20tough%20place%20to%20come%20and%20tour%20and%20I've%20said%20a%20lot%20over%20the%20last%20so%20many%20years%20that%20I'm%20not%20the%20first%20left-hander%20to%20struggle%20against%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Duckett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20one%20of%2C%20if%20not%20the%20best%20off-spinner%2C%20to%20have%20played%20the%20game.%20Obviously%20I%20went%20away%20and%20worked%20hard%20at%20my%20game%20and%20my%20defence.%20It's%20the%20backing%20of%20this%20team%20that%20means%20I%20can%20go%20out%20and%20play%20with%20the%20freedom%20that%20I%20did%20yesterday%2C%26quot%3B%20Duckett%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-handed%20batter%20said%20England%20did%20not%20rue%20much%20over%20their%20batting%20collapse%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20second%20session%2C%20in%20which%20they%20were%20shot%20out%20for%20319%20having%20resumed%20at%20290%2F5.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20obviously%20played%20well%20yesterday%2C%20but%20we%20had%20so%20much%20work%20to%20do%20today.%20But%20we're%20always%20positive.%20It%20did%20happen%20quite%20fast%2C%20there%20wasn't%20much%20time%20to%20have%20much%20emotion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStokesy%20(Ben%20Stokes)%20spoke%20to%20us%20before%20we%20went%20out%20to%20field%20and%20said%20he%20actually%20wanted%20us%20to%20get%20out%20today%20and%20have%20a%20bowl%20at%20them%20and%20get%20cracking%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708237320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F7ln5ih88_ben-duckett-afp_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fjaiswal-a-superstar-in-making-england-deserve-some-credit-for-inspiring-others-duckett-5076368%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20hit%20nine%20fours%20and%20five%20sixes%20in%20his%20133-ball%20104%20before%20retiring%20hurt%20due%20to%20back%20spasms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Esha%20Deol%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20runaway%20bride%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708237226000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107791832%2Cimgsize-38074.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fesha-deol-a-runaway-bride