https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fberlin-film-festival-african-cinema-rising-1235914839%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fberlin-film-festival-african-cinema-rising-1235914839%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fberlin-film-festival-african-cinema-rising-1235914839%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Jharkhand%20Congress%20MLAs%20Arrive%20In%20Delhi%2C%20Seek%20Removal%20Of%204%20Ministers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStrong%20resentment%20is%20brewing%20among%20a%20section%20of%20Congress%20legislators%20in%20Jharkhand%20over%20the%20induction%20of%20four%20party%20MLAs%20as%20ministers%20in%20the%20Champai%20Soren-led%20JMM%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2012%20MLAs%20of%20the%20party%20have%20threatened%20to%20boycott%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20session%20from%20February%2023%20and%20head%20to%20Jaipur%20if%20the%20ministers%20are%20not%20replaced%20by%20new%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20of%20the%2012%20disgruntled%20MLAs%20reached%20Delhi%20last%20evening%20to%20lodge%20their%20protest%20before%20the%20party%20high%20command%20over%20the%20induction%20of%20four%20party%20MLAs%20in%20the%20Champai%20Soren%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JMM-led%20alliance%20in%20the%20state%20has%2047%20MLAs%20(JMM%20has%2029%2C%20Congress%20has%2017%20and%20RJD%20has%20one)%20in%20the%2081-member%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnhappy%20over%20Congress'%20decision%20to%20give%20ministerial%20berths%20to%20Alamgir%20Alam%2C%20Rameshwar%20Oraon%2C%20Banna%20Gupta%20and%20Badal%20Patralekh%20again%2C%20the%20legislators%20went%20into%20a%20huddle%20at%20Ranchi%20Circuit%20House%20just%20before%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20on%20Friday%20with%20plans%20of%20boycotting%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20persuaded%20by%20Jharkhand%20Congress%20in-charge%20Ghulam%20Ahmed%20Mir%20and%20PCC%20chief%20Rajesh%20Thakur%2C%20the%20MLAs%20reached%20Raj%20Bhavan%20to%20attend%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20replacement%20of%20all%20the%20four...We%20the%2012%20MLAs%20are%20together%20right%20now%2C%20barring%20the%20four%20ministers%20and%20Pradeep%20Yadav.%20We%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20leadership%20to%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20our%20demand%20to%20change%20the%20four%20ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20a%20minister%20from%20each%20division%20to%20cover%20all%20the%20five%20divisions%20in%20the%20state.%20We%20also%20want%20implementation%20of%20the%20'one%20person%2C%20one%20post'%20rule%20made%20by%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%26quot%3B%20MLA%20Kumar%20Jaimangal%2C%20alias%20Anup%20Singh%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bermo%20legislator%20said%20if%20they%20fail%20to%20hear%20anything%20from%20the%20party's%20state%20and%20central%20leaderships%20soon%2C%20they%20will%20be%20forced%20to%20fly%20to%20the%20Rajasthan%20capital%20and%20boycott%20the%20budget%20session%20of%20Jharkhand%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20has%2017%20MLAs%20and%20the%20JMM%20(29).%20The%20JMM%20has%20already%20taken%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20speaker's%20posts.%20They%20have%20six%20ministerial%20berths%20and%20we%20want%20the%20remaining%20one.%20We%20are%20not%20compromising%20on%20that.%20In%20case%20Alamgir%20Alam%20is%20retained%2C%20he%20should%20quit%20the%20post%20of%20the%20Congress%20Legislature%20Party%20leader%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaimangal%20demanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20group%20of%2012%20MLAs%20have%20already%20handed%20over%20a%20signed%20letter%20to%20the%20party%20chief%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Mahagama%20MLA%20Dipika%20Pandey%20Singh%20told%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20the%20party%20to%20change%20the%20ministers%20and%20give%20opportunity%20to%20new%20faces.%20Instead%20of%20adding%20more%20womeswen%20faces%2C%20they%20have%20retained%20one%20woman%20minister...%20How%20do%20you%20justify%20that.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBebi%20Devi%2C%20excise%20minister%20in%20the%20previous%20Hemant%20Soren%20government%2C%20was%20given%20women%20and%20child%20development%20and%20social%20welfare%20portfolios.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevi%20had%20contested%20the%20Dumri%20bypoll%20in%202023%20after%20the%20death%20of%20her%20husband%20Jagannath%20Mahto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoba%20Manjhi%2C%20a%20senior%20JMM%20MLA%20from%20Manoharpur%2C%20who%20was%20the%20women%2C%20child%20development%20and%20social%20security%20minister%20in%20the%20Hemant%20Soren%20government%2C%20has%20been%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMandar%20Congress%20MLA%20Shilpi%20Neha%20Tirkey%2C%20too%2C%20voiced%20her%20discontent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20we%20had%20lots%20of%20disapproval%20and%20disappointments%20on%20the%20quota%20given%20to%20us...Since%20there%20was%20a%20sudden%20opportunity%20and%20a%20new%20cabinet%20was%20being%20formed%20under%20Champai%20Soren%20ji%2C%20everyone%20was%20hopeful%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20reshuffle%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInitially%2C%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20was%20scheduled%20on%20February%208.%20When%20it%20was%20postponed%2C%20we%20were%20assured%20that%20a%20reshuffle%20will%20happen.%20But%20it%20was%20very%20disappointing%20when%20we%20saw%20there%20was%20no%20change%20and%20those%20who%20were%20openly%20praising%20BJP%20were%20retained%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Tirkey%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20were%20new%20faces%20not%20given%20opportunity...%20that's%20why%20the%20whole%20revolt%20...We%20wanted%20to%20boycott%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%2C%20but%20our%20state%20in-charge%20promised%20that%20there%20will%20be%20a%20good%20discussion%20in%20Delhi%20about%20it....It%20is%20not%20about%20two%20or%20four%20MLAs...It%20is%2012%20legislators%20who%20are%20voicing%20it%20out%20together.%20You%20appoint%20anyone...You%20appoint%20community-wise%2C%20area-wise...We%20just%20want%20fresh%20faces...We%20want%20such%20faces%20who%20can%20fulfill%20people's%20aspirations.%20These%20ministers%20have%20not%20delivered%20in%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20what%20is%20the%20guarantee%20that%20they%20will%20deliver%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leadership%20has%20given%20an%20assurance%20it%20will%20discuss%20the%20issue%2C%20Ms%20Tirkey%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20to%20KC%20Venugopal%20that%20we%20want%20a%20discussion%20with%20senior%20leaders.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20Congress%20MLAs%20objected%20to%20the%20name%20of%20Banna%20Gupta%2C%20who%20had%20courted%20controversy%20recently%20after%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20posted%20a%20video%20purportedly%20showing%20him%20engaging%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bobscene%26quot%3B%20phone%20conversation%20with%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20termed%20the%20video%20%26quot%3Bfake%20and%20edited%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20state%20chief%20Rajesh%20Thakur%20told%20PTI%20that%20the%20issues%20flagged%20by%20the%2012%20Congress%20legislators%20are%20being%20looked%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20expressed%20their%20feelings%20to%20me%20and%20I%20shall%20bring%20this%20to%20the%20notice%20of%20the%20party%20central%20leadership.%20The%20decision%20by%20the%20central%20leadership%20will%20be%20accepted%20by%20all.%20We%20are%20hopeful%20of%20resolving%20it%20very%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2011-member%20Champai%20Soren%20cabinet%2C%20there%20are%20only%20two%20new%20faces%20-%20Basant%20Soren%2C%20JMM%20supremo%20Shibu%20Soren's%20youngest%20son%2C%20and%20JMM's%20Chaibasa%20MLA%20Deepak%20Birua.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20eight%20were%20sworn-in%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20chief%2