20frescos%2C%20a%20giant%20iconostasis%20that%20used%20422%20kilos%20of%20gold%2C%20and%20a%20main%20bell%20weighing%2024%20tonnes.%20Its%20interior%20was%20dazzling%20with%20gold%20silver%20and%20gems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goddess%20of%20history%20it%20seems%2C%20had%20her%20own%20plans.%20The%20Bolshevik%20Revolution%20happened%20in%201917%2C%20the%20czar%20and%20his%20family%20were%20exiled%20and%20then%20killed.%20And%20then%20in%201931%20the%20all-powerful%20leader%20Stalin%20decided%20to%20raze%20it%20and%20erase%20the%20memory%20of%20the%20temple%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20376px)%2085vw%2C%20376px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22376%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22458%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOvernight%20the%20temple%20was%20made%20out%20of%20bounds%2C%20surrounded%20by%20barbed%20wire.%20When%20the%20demolishers%20had%20done%20whatever%20they%20could%2C%20only%20the%20shell%20remained%20of%20the%20once%20magnificent%20temple.%20All%20gold%20and%20gems%20and%20silk%20and%20velvet%20vestments%20embroidered%20with%20gold%20and%20silver%20threads%20were%20removed%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cycle%20of%20erection%20and%20after%20some%20time%20shattering%20of%20grand%20places%20of%20worship%20and%20then%20again%20their%20re-erection%20has%20a%20long%20history%20in%20the%20world.%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20latest%20city%20to%20be%20re-energised%20by%20the%20building%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20too%20has%20been%20through%20this%20cycle.%20Today%20few%20know%20that%20the%20holy%20site%20even%20pre-dates%20Ram.%20The%20Atharva%20Veda%20(second%20chapter)%20calls%20Ayodhya%20by%20its%20earlier%20Buddhist%20name%2C%20Saket.%20Buddhist%20text%20Divyavadaan%20corroborates%20this%20and%20says%20that%20Saket%20%C2%A0created%20itself%20(%3Cem%3ESvayamagata%2C%20swayamagata%20Saket%20iti%20uchyate%3C%2Fem%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ancient%20folklore%2C%20the%20city%20that%20King%20Dashrath%20had%20built%20was%20buried%20under%20Sita%E2%80%99s%20curse.%20Several%20centuries%20later%20it%20was%20rediscovered%20by%20King%20Vikramaditya%20through%20a%20dream%20wherein%20the%20goddess%20of%20the%20city%20requested%20him%20to%20unearth%20her%20city.%20The%20king%20had%20it%20dug%20out%20from%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20earth.%20%C2%A0The%20vast%20pan-Indian%20popularity%20of%20the%20cult%20of%20Ram%20and%20Ayodhya%20as%20his%20holy%20birth%20place%20began%20only%20in%20the%2014th%20century%20with%20the%20Bhakti%20movement%20and%20its%20arrival%20up%20north%20in%20latter%20half%20of%2016th%3Cspan%3E%20century%3C%2Fspan%3E%20CE.%20Thereafter%20the%20Vaishnavite%20Ramanand%20sect%20and%20saint%20poet%20Tulsidas%20popularised%20it%20by%20their%20devotional%20poetry%20that%20portrayed%20Lord%20Ram%20of%20Ayodhya%20as%20the%20ideal%20Man-God%20(%3Cem%3EMaya%20Manushyam%20Hari%3C%2Fem%3E).%20Linking%20this%20with%20the%20recent%20makeover%20of%20Ayodhya%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20and%20its%20formal%20installation%20of%20an%20idol%20of%20Ram%20as%20a%20young%20boy%20on%20January%2022%20is%20actually%20a%20journey%20into%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEstablishing%20an%20area%20as%20a%20holy%20spot%20and%20building%20and%20rebuilding%20monuments%20needs%20clever%20negotiators%20and%20publicists.%20So%20after%20the%20Ram%20cult%20got%20going%2C%20Hanumangarhi%2C%20the%20fortress%20of%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%20emissary%2C%20came%20up%20and%20by%20the%2018th%20century%20became%20the%20natural%20meeting%20place%20for%20representatives%20of%20a%20slowly%20dying%20monarchy%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20empowered%20Awadh%20Durbar%20and%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20officials.%20All%20made%20important%20power-sharing%20deals%20with%20local%20mercenaries%20and%20bands%20of%20armed%20%3Cem%3Esadhus%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22In%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20Hailing%2C%20Sita%20Was%20Forgotten.%20Her%20Revival%20Would%20Have%20Symbolised%20Healing%20for%20Men%20and%20Women%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fin-rams-hailing-sita-was-forgotten-her-revival-would-have-symbolised-healing-for-men-and-women%5C%22%3EIn%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20Hailing%2C%20Sita%20Was%20Forgotten.%20Her%20Revival%20Would%20Have%20Symbolised%20Healing%20for%20Men%20and%20Women%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20rebuilding%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20at%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20birthplace%20began%20as%20an%20idea%20with%20immense%20political%20potential%20in%201992%2C%20the%20year%20of%20razing%20of%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20said%20to%20have%20been%20built%20by%20a%20general%2C%20Mir%20Baki%2C%20who%20had%20replaced%20an%20existing%20temple%20to%20build%20a%20mosque%20named%20after%20the%20victorious%20Mughal%20king%20Babar.%20Since%201992%2C%20Ayodhya%20became%20a%20political%20petridish%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20mega%202019%20victory%20in%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20rhetoric%20turned%20towards%20erecting%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebhavya%2C%20navya%2C%20divya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(grand%2C%20new%20and%20holy)%20temple%20there%20to%20Ram%2C%20both%20by%20way%20of%20thanksgiving%20and%20declaring%20the%20imminent%20arrival%20of%20a%20Hindutva-driven%20state.%20Soon%20it%20got%20the%20necessary%20judicial%20green%20signal%20to%20go%20ahead.%20Work%20was%20then%20speeded%20up%20to%20try%20and%20coincide%20the%20opening%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20January%202024%20with%20general%20election%20rallies%20scheduled%20just%20a%20few%20months%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20aided%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%2C%20led%20everything%20from%20the%20front%20and%20at%20the%20installation%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Balak%20Ram%20statue%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20Ram%20Lalla%20has%20returned%20after%20500%20years%20to%20his%20rightful%20place.%20As%20conch%20shells%20sounded%20and%20a%20thousand%20throats%20sang%20%3Cem%3Ebhajans%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%20was%20repeated%20again%20and%20again%20that%20Hindutva%20was%20the%20future%20and%20the%20core%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20would%20draw%20thousands%20of%20pilgrims%20from%20not%20just%20India%20but%20also%20foreign%20lands%20where%20diaspora%20Hindus%20still%20follow%20Hindutva.%20It%20was%20also%20underscored%20forcefully%20how%20this%20would%20invite%20capital%20investment%20in%20the%20state%20and%20Ayodhya%20in%20particular%20and%20generate%20jobs%20and%20opportunities%20for%20entrepreneurs%20and%20the%20tourist%20industry%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20who%20hail%20from%20Uttarakhand%2C%20recently%20christened%20Dev%20Bhumi%2C%20learnt%20early%20on%20how%20this%20works.%20The%20new%20pilgrims%20are%20religious%20tourists.%20The%20pilgrims%20had%20been%20coming%20to%20Ayodhya%20even%20earlier%2C%20but%20they%20were%20mostly%20simple%20rural%20folk%20or%20a%20few%20old%20couples%20with%20limited%20spending%20power%20and%20not%20much%20interest%20in%20worldly%20pursuits.%20The%20new%20tourists%20are%20young%20and%20will%20visit%20round%20the%20year%20in%20droves%20provided%20that%20pilgrimage%20trails%20have%20been%20made%20user%20friendly.%20No%20more%20smelly%20dharmshalas%20with%20bed%20bugs%20and%20bad%20food%20and%20temperamental%20Pandas%20for%20them.%20Photos%20of%20hotels%20and%20home%20stays%2C%20spas%20and%20food%20courts%20all%20along%20the%20routes%20must%20be%20available%20online%20for%20%E2%80%98customers%E2%80%99%20before%20the%20group%20bookings%20begin.%20And%20yes%2C%20it%20will%20bring%20in%20heap%20big%20bucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20new%20species%20of%20pilgrims%20has%20also%20changed%20religion%20into%20an%20industry%20that%20follows%20pilgrims%E2%80%99%20algorithms%20keenly%20and%20creates%20bespoke%20exclusive%20packages.%20Old-style%20darshan%20and%20immersion%20in%20holy%20rivers%20are%20pass%C3%A9.%20The%20bespoke%20packages%20promise%20you%20%E2%80%9Ca%20mystic%20experience%20of%20a%20temple%2Fcity%20old-as-time!%E2%80%9D%20along%20with%20chances%20to%20do%20a%20bit%20of%20river%20rafting%20and%20air%20diving.%20The%20tourism%20promoters%20hand%20you%20addresses%20and%20coupons%20for%20buying%20souvenirs%20and%20holy%20waters%20and%20%3Cem%3Eprasadam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20even%20send%20you%20maps%20dotted%20with%20selfie%20points.%20And%20of%20course%2C%20should%20the%20customers%20so%20wish%2C%20there%20will%20be%20camera%20crew%20available%20to%20capture%20the%20pilgrims%E2%80%99%20waggish%20ego.%20Honoured%20pilgrim%2Ftourists%20face%20none%20of%20the%20earlier%20multiple%20checkings%20by%20petty%20officials%20or%20long%20waits%20at%20toll%20plazas.%20Difficulties%2C%20as%20and%20when%20they%20arise%2C%20can%20be%20easily%20negotiated%20with%20some%20exchange%20of%20money%20and%20flashing%20official%20(read%20party)%20badges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22When%20Ravan%20Triumphs%20in%20Ayodhya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhen-ravan-triumphs-in-ayodhya%5C%22%3EWhen%20Ravan%20Triumphs%20in%20Ayodhya%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20is%20still%20out%20on%20whether%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20and%20sundry%20others%20who%20have%20already%20bought%20properties%20to%20go%20live%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20will%20actually%20stay%20there.%20But%20the%20millennial%20pilgrims%E2%80%99%20progress%20in%20the%20age%20of%20global%20meltdowns%2C%20works%20along%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20Amritkaal%20economy%20that%20has%20hard-wired%20them%20for%20planning%20for%20the%20coming%20year%20as%20they%20don%20their%20itinerant%20pilgrims%E2%80%99%20robes%20and%20get%20into%20their%20SUVs%20or%20leave%20for%20the%20newly%20built%20airport.%20Damn%20the%20carbon%20footprints%20or%20local%20water%20shortages%20that%20are%20routine%20now%20in%20temple%20towns.%20The%20neo-converts%20to%20Hindutva%3A%20scientists%20and%20engineers%2C%20doctors%2C%20IT%20czars%20and%20environmentalists%2C%20both%20desi%20and%20NRI%2C%20are%20all%20happy%20singing%20and%20partying%20to%20pop%20bhajans.%20The%20built%20in%20obsolescence%20within%20such%20tourism%20models%20does%20not%20interest%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttarakhand%2C%20we%20see%20the%20results%20clearly.%20As%20more%20and%20more%20pilgrims%20flock%20to%20Gangotri%20and%20Yamunotri%2C%20the%20glaciers%C2%A0%20recede.%20The%20broader%20the%20roads%2C%20the%20bigger%20the%20landslides%20during%20monsoons.%20Snow%20has%20already%20thinned%20to%20a%20stop%20in%20the%20entire%20Himalayan%20region.%20So%20watch%20out%2C%20Ayodhya%3B%20if%20you%20do%20not%20watch%20out%2C%20the%20place%20will%20lose%20its%20endearing%C2%A0%20informality%20and%20become%20another%20industrial%20city%20inviting%20skyscrapers%2C%20vast%20traffic%20jams%20and%20malls%20with%20food%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverybody%20knows%20this%2C%20but%20we%20are%20still%20witnessing%20the%20genetic%20inability%20of%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20powerful%20to%20deny%20the%20alarming%20reality%20of%20global%20warming.%20Inaugurating%20the%20first%20grand%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20built%20by%20the%20BAPS%20(Swamin%20Narayan%20sect)%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpriest%20of%20Ma%20Bharati%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20added%20how%20the%20grand%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20has%20enhanced%20Ayodhya%20joy.%20The%20BAPS%2C%20he%20predicted%2C%20will%20be%20a%20centre%20of%20communal%20ha