a.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341973%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20has%20helped%20175%20students%20get%20their%20dream%20university.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbitio%20began%20with%20a%20core%20challenge%20we%20aimed%20to%20address%3A%20simplifying%20the%20admissions%20process%20for%20students%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20developed%20a%20platform%20product%20designed%20to%20support%20students%20throughout%20their%20entire%20admissions%20journey.%20Our%20ultimate%20objective%20is%20to%20establish%20a%20comprehensive%20global%20AI%20admissions%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CRegardless%20of%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20background%20or%20location%2C%20our%20aim%20is%20to%20provide%20equal%20opportunities%20and%20access%20to%20the%20right%20guidance%2C%20a%20privilege%20often%20reserved%20for%20the%20affluent%20or%20those%20able%20to%20afford%20expensive%20counsellors.%20We%20leverage%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F126973%2Fkerala-police-equips-personnel-cutting-edge-body-cameras%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting-edge%20technology%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20AI%2C%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20AI%20comes%20into%20play%20with%20the%20process%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20employ%20AI%20in%20two%20primary%20areas.%20Firstly%2C%20we%20utilise%20it%20to%20assist%20students%20in%20determining%20the%20most%20suitable%20program%20or%20university%20currently%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20While%20there%20are%20existing%20filtration%20tools%20enabling%20students%20to%20filter%20courses%20they%20are%20eligible%20for%20and%20view%20them%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20an%20additional%20step%20forward.%20We%20incorporate%20preferences%20into%20the%20equation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20AI%20strives%20to%20understand%20and%20integrate%20the%20individual%20preferences%20of%20each%20student%20into%20the%20recommendations%20that%20it%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20accomplish%20this%20through%20our%20proprietary%20recommendation%20engine%2C%20which%20has%20been%20trained%20on%20over%2015%20million%20acceptance%20and%20admit%20data%20points.%20While%20it%E2%80%99s%20certainly%20possible%20for%20students%20to%20conduct%20this%20research%20themselves%20by%20visiting%20numerous%20websites%2C%20reading%20various%20articles%2C%20and%20compiling%20the%20information%20manually%2C%20our%20platform%20streamlines%20this%20process%20significantly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20synthesising%20and%20analysing%20vast%20amounts%20of%20information%2C%20the%20platform%20can%20deliver%20personalised%20recommendations%20quickly%20and%20seamlessly%2C%20saving%20students%20valuable%20time%20and%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20where%20AI%20comes%20in%20to%20help%20the%20students%20is%20writing%20their%20personal%20essays.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20students%20know%20what%20college%20they%20want%2C%20the%20next%20step%20is%20to%20write%20a%20stellar%20essay.%20We%20trained%20our%20model%20with%205%2C000%20accepted%20essays%20from%20across%20universities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20begin%20by%20ensuring%20basic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341068%2Fteach-spoken-english-on-youtube-dehati-madam-uttar-pradesh-yashoda-lodhi-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egram