Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341947%2Funiversity-admission-counselling-abroad-ambitio-startup-ai-dream-college-uk-us-canada-iit%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Startup%20Is%20Building%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98First%20Green%20Hydrogen%20Plant%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20hydrogen%20is%20being%20heavily%20used%20in%20powering%20vehicles%2C%20oil%20refining%2C%20ammonia%20production%2C%20steel%20production%2C%20and%20to%20generate%20electricity.%20All%20of%20this%20hydrogen%20is%20supplied%20using%20fossil%20fuels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Freports%2Fthe-future-of-hydrogen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Energy%20Agency%20%3C%2Fa%3E(IEA)%2C%20the%20production%20of%20hydrogen%20is%20responsible%20for%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%20of%20around%20830%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20per%20year.%20Interestingly%2C%20green%20hydrogen%20%E2%80%93%20produced%20by%20the%20electrolysis%20of%20water%20using%20renewable%20electricity%20%E2%80%93%20could%20save%20tonnes%20of%20this%20carbon%20dioxide%20emitted%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tap%20into%20green%20hydrogen%E2%80%99s%20potential%20and%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20a%20clean%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20affordable%20energy%20future%2C%20Haryana-based%20green%20hydrogen%20company%2C%20Hygenco%2C%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20would%20be%20the%20first%20operative%20green%20hydrogen%20production%20facility%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20will%20produce%20energy%20without%20emitting%20carbon%20dioxide%20into%20the%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20