%20responsibility%20will%20the%20children%20be%20if%20there%20is%20no%20marriage%20in%20place%3F%20But%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20senior%20citizens%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20%5Bmuch%5D%20scope%20for%20this%20problem%20to%20arise.%20Their%20children%20are%20settled%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20all%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323097%2Fpune-man-starts-yodda-elder-care-startup-for-emergency-help-to-senior-citizens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esenior%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20has%20assisted%20in%20finding%20the%20right%20partner%20are%20financially%20stable.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20property%20disputes%20do%20not%20arise%20as%20there%20is%20no%20legal%20binding%20between%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20Happy%20Seniors%20began%20its%20journey%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20seniors%20looking%20for%20love.%20The%20group%20met%20every%20month%20and%20during%20the%20first%20%E2%80%98picnic%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20first%20match%20was%20made.%20A%20couple%2C%20the%20woman%20in%20her%20fifties%20and%20the%20man%20in%20his%20sixties%2C%20fell%20in%20love%20and%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdate%E2%80%9D.%20A%20year%20later%20they%20got%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG-20240214-WA0005-1707912941.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20members%20of%20Happy%20Seniors%20meet%20every%20two%20months%20and%20Madhav%20Damle%2C%20the%20founder%2C%20says%20there%20are%20almost%2020%20new%20members%20at%20each%20meeting%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG-20240214-WA0005-1707912941.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuplo